{"ne30:0.1":"Netti ","ne30:0.2":"Patiniddesavara ","ne30:0.3":"Sampata 11 ","ne30:0.4":"Pannattiharasampata ","ne30:1.1":"Tattha katamo pannattiharasampato? ","ne30:2.1":"“Tasma rakkhitacittassa, sammasankappagocaro”ti gatha. ","ne30:2.2":"“Tasma rakkhitacittassa”ti padatthanapannatti satiya. ","ne30:2.3":"“Sammasankappagocaro”ti bhavanapannatti samathassa. ","ne30:2.4":"“Sammaditthipurekkharo, natvana udayabbayan”ti dassanabhumiya nikkhepapannatti. ","ne30:2.5":"“Thinamiddhabhibhu bhikkhu”ti samudayassa anavasesappahanapannatti, “sabba duggatiyo jahe”ti bhavanapannatti maggassa. ","ne30:2.6":"Niyutto pannattiharasampato. "}